# Raw Clinic Web (monorepo)

Next.js monorepo: **hub** (`apps/hub`, GitHub Pages) + **rawclinic** (`apps/rawclinic`, Vercel) share **`packages/shared`**.

Hub routes (`/`, `/blog`, legal, feedback) use **gray** accent via `resolveThemeAccent` in `packages/shared/config/app-theme.ts` — do not hardcode hub accent in components.

## Two UI layers

| Layer | Where | Styling |
|-------|--------|---------|
| **Landing / marketing** | `AppLandingPage`, `.landing` | `styles/landing*.scss`, metal surfaces, `LandingReveal` |
| **Utility** | FAQ, legal, feedback, roadmap, blog | Radix `Container size="2"`, `styles/prose.scss`, `site-page-hero.scss` |

Prefer **extending existing shared pieces** over new one-off layouts.

## Reuse before creating

- **Hero**: `SitePageHero` (utility); `AppLegalHero` (legal); landing hero blocks stay in `AppLandingPage` / `landing.scss`
- **App cards**: `HomeAppCard` + `homeAppCardFromHomeData` / `homeAppCardFromAppConfig`
- **Feature grids**: `LandingPrimaryGrid` — variants `featured` \| `panel` \| `compact` (not inline duplicate grids)
- **CTA**: `AppContactCta`
- **Images**: `OptimizedImage`
- **Long copy**: `className="site-prose"` on Radix `Container`

## Imports & paths

- Use `@/` alias in **packages/shared** (`@/components/...`, `@/lib/...`, `@/config/...`)
- App routes in `apps/hub` or `apps/rawclinic` import shared code via the same `@/` path (tsconfig maps to `packages/shared`)
- Config/content: `packages/shared/config/`, `packages/shared/config/home-content.ts`, etc.
- Do not reintroduce removed modules: `LandingHero`, `DescriptionText`, `RoadmapOverviewCard`

## Scope

Minimal diffs; match existing naming (BEM-ish: `landing-primary-grid__`, `home-page__`). New global SCSS → add `@use` in `styles/index.scss`.
